								<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the religious concept.  For the American grunge band, see <a href="/wiki/Nirvana_(band)" title="Nirvana (band)">Nirvana (band)</a>.  For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Nirvana_(disambiguation)" title="Nirvana (disambiguation)">Nirvana (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
