<p><span style="color:#005e07; background-color:#F4C430; font-size:11px"><a href="/wiki/Puranas" title="Puranas">Puranas</a></span></p>
<ul>
<li><i>Brahma puranas</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Brahma_Purana" title="Brahma Purana">Brahma</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Brahm%C4%81nda_Purana" title="Brahmānda Purana" class="mw-redirect">Brahmanda</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Brahma_Vaivarta_Purana" title="Brahma Vaivarta Purana">Brahmavaivarta</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/M%C4%81rkandeya_Purana" title="Mārkandeya Purana" class="mw-redirect">Markandeya</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Bhavishya_Purana" title="Bhavishya Purana">Bhavishya</a></li>
